      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-02-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-06-06T19:01:08Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Commercial Remote Sensing Amendment Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies provisions relating to the licensing of commercial remote sensing systems.</p> <p>The bill decreases from 120 to 60 days the amount of time in which the Department of Commerce shall review and make a determination on the application for a license by a private sector party to operate a private remote sensing space system.</p> <p>The annual report concerning the licensing of private remote sensing systems must include (1) a list of all applications, listed by tier, as well as the rationale for each tier categorization; and (2) all terms, conditions, or restrictions placed on licensees.</p>  ]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>07</versionCode>
